{"tid":1397252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【八五罷工】唔該你班撚樣唔好再跪係到求人！","createTime":"2019-08-02T11:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T12:16:08.000Z","uid":220356,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a69b39c1cec4ff840fc38cf560fa60bc3a4b8c","tid":1397252,"uid":220356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"我知巴絲你地出發點係好，<br />\n想更多人出黎集會同罷工，<br />\n<br />\n但唔該唔好再跪係地下求人去集會/遊行，<br />\n我地唔係失敗者啊，我地跟本無做錯到，<br />\n唔使咁低賤跪係地到求人去架！明唔撚明啊！？<br />\n<br />\n前線手足打生打死，你地就跪係地到好似自己做錯咁求人，你哋知唔知你哋呢種行為，係侮辱左成班前線啊！醒下啦！文宣唔係咁樣要人地認同架！<br />\n<br />\n最後一句：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b6d37f22782c75b25bba45abee83b9ff6fb5e17f","tid":1397252,"uid":76089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a24a4bfb700d8482ece0a92444c9ff2f1d88567","tid":1397252,"uid":220356,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"利申見到一個屌一個，係咪奴性重到傻撚左啊！"},{"pid":"fc2a9fef9b2f5121a36fce01d28bd300b0b3f647","tid":1397252,"uid":220356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n9PPWPh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn9PPWPh.png&h=81d861c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8Vb99h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8Vb99h.png&h=02a68aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8QPHxnD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8QPHxnD.png&h=e8a8f95b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jAjsJui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjAjsJui.png&h=4f7fbba2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"046fef815a4ca54e7515bff00bc3094f200d4ab4","tid":1397252,"uid":220356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:44:24.000Z","m